title: Jazz Jack Rabbit (1994)
description:
This is is the original Jazz Jack Rabbit Installer I found from a retro gaming site a while back. I Figured I would contribute to the community and allow this forgotten classic to be played without jumping any hoops or having to use any complex emulators and what not.

The installer is quite simple. This is A full game installer with dosbox built right in, so its very simple to use, works for me with windows 7 64 bit, tested with Microsoft security essentials and clean of any viruses. (ps My first torrent.)

JazzJackRabbit forever!
